{"tid":1665533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵：西鐵綫元朗站明日(21日)下午2時起臨時關閉","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T16:42:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e88181080141cc750333bc3425e9bcd6981acc01","tid":1665533,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"除機場快綫外，港鐵各綫、輕鐵及港鐵巴士今天的服務時間已經完結。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，經審視復修工作的進度，並與相關政府部門進行風險評估後，明天除機場快綫外的港鐵各綫、輕鐵及港鐵巴士服務將提早於晚上10時結束。另外，西鐵綫元朗站會於下午2時起臨時關閉，乘客請預早計劃行程及考慮使用其他交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487313-20191020.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487313-20191020.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=a296fa5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487313-20191020.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=744bc462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487313-20191020.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5489a1f15077e6bdb66bcec9ef9fc0873861edc8","tid":1665533,"uid":276530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e88181080141cc750333bc3425e9bcd6981acc01","tid":1665533,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"除機場快綫外，港鐵各綫、輕鐵及港鐵巴士今天的服務時間已經完結。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，經審視復修工作的進度，並與相關政府部門進行風險評估後，明天除機場快綫外的港鐵各綫、輕鐵及港鐵巴士服務將提早於晚上10時結束。另外，西鐵綫元朗站會於下午2時起臨時關閉，乘客請預早計劃行程及考慮使用其他交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487313-20191020.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487313-20191020.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=a296fa5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487313-20191020.